Haverty Furniture Companies, Inc. Key Developments

Haverty Furniture Companies, Inc. Reports Sales Results for the Second Quarter and Six Months Ended June 30, 2017
Jul 7 17
Haverty Furniture Companies, Inc. reported sales results for the second quarter and six months ended June 30, 2017. For the quarter, the company reported that sales increased 1.1% to $196.8 million, compared with $194.8 million for the second quarter of 2016. On a comparable store basis, sales for the quarter were down 0.2%. Comparable store sales do not include locations opened, closed or otherwise non-comparable during the last 12 months.

For six months, the company reported sales of $397.3 million as compared to $389.3 million for the same period last year.


Haverty Furniture Companies, Inc. to Report Q2, 2017 Sales/Trading Statement Results on Jul 10, 2017
Jul 4 17
Haverty Furniture Companies, Inc. announced that they will report Q2, 2017 sales/trading statement results Pre-Market on Jul 10, 2017


