Company Summary
Haverty Furniture Companies, Inc. is a full-service home furnishings retailer.  The company operates showrooms in contiguous southern and central states.  Havertys provides its customers with a wide selection of furniture and accessories primarily in the middle to upper-middle price ranges.  As an added convenience to its customers, the company offers financing through a revolving charge credit plan.   





 













